{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/algorithm/23-majority-element/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Soobing","author":"[Soobin Bak]","siteUrl":"https://soobing.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"soobing/soobing.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"soobing"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"61cd7b85-30df-5791-b0d0-b27560a1b3b5","excerpt":"5월은 날씨따라 한없이 풀어지는구나~~ 오늘의 문제는 n/2이상 나온 수를 찾는 문제.\neasy해 easy해 너무너무 쉬워요~ 문제 요약 n/2이상 나온 수를 찾기(n/2이상 나오는 수는 항상 있음) 배운 것 에서 순회할 때는 key값으로 순회한다.  value가 궁금하면 로 접근해서 얻어낸다.","html":"<p>5월은 날씨따라 한없이 풀어지는구나~~</p>\n<p>오늘의 <a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/majority-element/\">문제</a>는 n/2이상 나온 수를 찾는 문제.\neasy해 easy해 너무너무 쉬워요~</p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-요약\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD\" aria-label=\"문제 요약 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 요약</h1>\n<p>n/2이상 나온 수를 찾기(n/2이상 나오는 수는 항상 있음)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">/**\n * @param {number[]} nums\n * @return {number}\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">majorityElement</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">nums</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> obj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>num <span class=\"token keyword\">of</span> nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>num<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>num<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>num<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> key <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>key<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span> nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> key\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"배운-것\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%B0%EC%9A%B4-%EA%B2%83\" aria-label=\"배운 것 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>배운 것</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">for...in</code>에서 순회할 때는 key값으로 순회한다. </li>\n<li>value가 궁금하면 <code class=\"language-text\">object[key]</code>로 접근해서 얻어낸다.</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"👛majority element","date":"May 07, 2020","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"src":"/static/8f2e76c531b063cb357f6521033e40dc/14b42/majority-element.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/algorithm/23-majority-element/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/22-number-complement/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🌹Number Complement","category":"algorithm","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/24-valid-perfect-square/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Valid Perfect Square","category":"algorithm","draft":false}}}}}